Polynomial bases

using HelFEM, Plots
let xs = range(-1, 1, length=2001)
    a = @animate for nnodes = 2:15
        b = HelFEM.PolynomialBasis(:legendre, nnodes)
        ys = b(xs)
        plot(xs, ys, label=false, title="Legendre, nnodes=$nnodes")
    end
    gif(a, fps=0.5)
end

Reference

HelFEM.PolynomialBasis — Type
struct PolynomialBasis

Wrapper type for the helfem::atomic::polynomial_basis::PolynomialBasis class, representing a set of polynomials $\{p_i(x)\}$ on a domain $x \in [-1, 1]$.
